Class CyclicReportOrder

java.lang.Object
  org.apertereports.model.CyclicReportOrder

@Entity
public class CyclicReportOrder
extends Object

A persistent representation of a cyclic report generation order. The entries are held in the public schema in a table named ar_cyclic_report_order.
